          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "I wish to preface this review with a statement that I didn’t play this game when it was originally released back in 2003 (this is actually my first experience with it), so nostalgia for this game shouldn’t play a factor in this review. I was more into ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Star Wars Battlefront ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "at the time, which was much more accessible to a five-year-old.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Originally released in 2003, riding a wave of new fandom inspired by the release of the ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Star Wars",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " prequels, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " was quickly regarded as a masterpiece and spawned a decade of sequels and expansions. Fans certainly have the warm fuzzies for this game but the bar for what makes a game good has changed in 18 years, so with its most recent re-release on the Nintendo Switch, it falls into the critique spotlight once more.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YixsKTtPNmc",
        "html": "<iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/YixsKTtPNmc?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>",
        "metadata": {
          "title": "STAR WARS: Knights of the Old Republic - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch",
          "author_name": "Nintendo",
          "author_url": "https://www.youtube.com/c/nintendo",
          "height": 113,
          "width": 200,
          "version": "1.0",
          "provider_name": "YouTube",
          "provider_url": "https://www.youtube.com/",
