            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", the nostalgia that the fandom has for this game is justified. The gameplay is dated but still very fun (I think “retro” is the best word here), the characters/dialogue feels like classic ",
